What about adding a template filter along the lines of:

```python
@app.template_filter('u')
def tounicode(val):
    if isinstance(val, str):
         return val.decode('utf8')
     return val
```

Then we can easily fix problems in the templates by:

```jinja
{{ myvar|u }}
```

