@gastlich,

The issue is each call does something a bit different. storage_client.bucket creates a bucket object on the client. storage_client.create_bucket creates the bucket on the platform. When you changed your code to use bucket() you changed it to not actually create anything until you had set the location to EU.

In the original you had created a bucket in US and then tried to change its location to EU. Once created, you cannot change the location of a bucket.

